## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+
- npm or yarn
- A Web3 wallet (e.g., MetaMask)

### Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusernam/manga-bot-frontend.git
cd manga-bot-frontend
npm install
```

### Development
```bash
npm run dev
```

### Build
```bash
npm run build
```

